Hah!

64
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,720
And so...

65
00:04:47,010 --> 00:04:49,850
Christmas Day arrived.

66
00:04:51,710 --> 00:04:54,500
First up, the preliminary battle on the 24th.

67
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,830
The entire day,

68
