78
00:05:28,290 --> 00:05:29,430
Thanks!

79
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:32,180
Want some tea?

80
00:05:33,590 --> 00:05:35,830
With the money I earned from my gig on the 24th,

81
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:38,790
