84
00:05:44,890 --> 00:05:48,220
Plus, I got to show Ayato
what a great big brother I am.

85
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:49,550
All in all, not bad.

86
00:05:54,030 --> 00:05:55,030
And just like that,

87
00:05:56,580 --> 00:06:01,230
